    "name": "Tabletop Shop Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3328620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your love for tabletop games into a thriving business, where every shelf, dice, and customer tells a story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stock your shelves, host board game sessions, craft your own games, and build a shop loved by collectors and gamers alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/29df5c5ef933a0e998c0762022e05798.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell themed figures to complete collections and unlock unique dioramas and rewards. Completed collections increase your shop's appeal and value.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/9f0e5bfa59e369427834e32cae148cc3.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/9f0e5bfa59e369427834e32cae148cc3.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/9f0e5bfa59e369427834e32cae148cc3.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/2b8b3294dd9b207756edf0680ab4ca9d.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up game tables, craft your own board games from collected components, and host play sessions to earn extra income and attract dedicated players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/59b516fc2f188f97d044747842b49f59.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/59b516fc2f188f97d044747842b49f59.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/59b516fc2f188f97d044747842b49f59.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/ef1a1c2e38cf1d698e7532cd55babfb8.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Build, move, and arrange your shelves the way you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design a layout that fits your style and keeps your store efficient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/ab4f74003c3410506b6f865afb3660aa.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/ab4f74003c3410506b6f865afb3660aa.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/ab4f74003c3410506b6f865afb3660aa.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/aeb67cbe2669a64a7f26988428d81391.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Unpack deliveries and place your products with care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize your inventory smartly to keep customers happy and your store efficient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/5c2c9ff4a62eded03dd163cf1572c9ac.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/5c2c9ff4a62eded03dd163cf1572c9ac.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/5c2c9ff4a62eded03dd163cf1572c9ac.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/fc953332a367d4baec31dce1a9634ef9.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Level up to unlock new licenses, products, and expand your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level brings fresh opportunities and deeper gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/d24ce23cc27adfc6d3c7cad5ccdbbc38.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/d24ce23cc27adfc6d3c7cad5ccdbbc38.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/d24ce23cc27adfc6d3c7cad5ccdbbc38.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/f2a3fd4bc5b6dc5565c35527fa73be49.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Don’t let the mess drive customers away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your mop to keep the store spotless and earn cleaner feedback.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/04d305e07999c2140c88dc2b9efd353f.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/04d305e07999c2140c88dc2b9efd353f.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/04d305e07999c2140c88dc2b9efd353f.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/0ef04cd2e29e595ea2a8c86309bc2ff6.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smelly store? Customers won’t stay long.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use sprays and fans to remove odor and maintain a fresh shopping environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/346527f0324ab19794f45f7764c2a173.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/346527f0324ab19794f45f7764c2a173.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/346527f0324ab19794f45f7764c2a173.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/7494f1cc01ebee3c9ef5428e48c637f7.avif?t=1771423780\" width=800 height=100 /></span>Keep the game tables clean between sessions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tidy environment makes your store the perfect hangout spot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/3e6ba107bf87686294a889ab936a6f64.poster.avif?t=1771423780\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/3e6ba107bf87686294a889ab936a6f64.webm?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328620/extras/3e6ba107bf87686294a889ab936a6f64.mp4?t=1771423780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
